{"type": "article", "id": 18309, "title": "可携带浴缸", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-01T07:20:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134801ArX6s3FWUEzPM2BZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可携带的浴缸，它有 7 公斤重。打开前是 8.5 毫米厚的椭圆形框架，白色的布料和水管都折叠在框架中，非常方便跟车携带。按照圆框结构拆开后就成了一个简易的浴缸，只要接上水就可以使用了。德国工业设计师 Carina Deuschl 因此获得了今年的红点奖，目前还没有上市。<a href=\"http://www.carina-deuschl.com/portfolio-item/xtend/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134759uFR1DPEb4lsJcqWS.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"822\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347596Fc45orPUCdgl1JS.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134800To4CXLq9dE0McSYB.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134800EW6SsKVLNxUZ7bCa.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"357\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.34\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134801EU3daAPWuLi0BGbV.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"753\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}